Import classes              = Alt+Enter
Auto code completion        = ctrl+space
param completion            = ctrl+p
View source code            = ctrl+left click
View Java doc               = crtl+Q
Rename refactor             = Shift+F6
quick find a class          = ctrl+n
show available methods      = ctrl+F12
To find or class            = CTRL+N - Then start tying the class name
find a test/methoD/variable = Ctrl+shift+Alt+N - Then start typing the name of the test
Find a file                 = Ctrl+Shift+N

